parameters.description:
It indicates how the value can be used to determine if the device is healthy:
* _value_refresh_rate_ means that we can base on the frequency at which new values are generated;
* _different_values_ means that we can base on the variability of values;
* _value_bounds_ means that we can base on the belonging of generated values to a given range of values.

_Required for actions:_ insert, update, update_temporary_event_values_for_registered_devices.
